    "S4 =\"A1, B1, B2, \" is the final solution of the solution tree.",
    "To better evaluate LLM's ability to complete tasks and follow instructions, we propose two metrics: Task completion measures whether the solution can successfully complete the task.",
    "If the solution finally provides a meaningful answer, mark it as \"Pass\".",
    "If the solution exceeds the max number of rounds or decides to restart, mark it as \"Not Pass\".",
    "Instruction-following measures whether the solution follows the user instruction."
  ],
